elements.name: To verify whether user is able to register a new online account for a measured property via ribbon (Address is not listed Account Number unknown / Payment Method Known ebilling option = No Marketing Preferences = Yes)

steps.name: User open the browser "edge" and launch the url "https://td-prep.nwl.co.uk/"
User clicks on Login or Create an account from Ribbon Account and should redirected to login tab
User clicks Create an account tab and should redirected to Create an account tab
System gets the required information from CC&B for the account "0020400200" using "allak" and "Monda16!"
User enters the account details on the Create an account screen "Test@1234"
User clicks on  Create account button and System should display the success screen popup to verify the user account
User opens "https://yopmail.com/en/" and enters the email address
User clicks on the activation mail to activate the account
User should be redirected to NWL Website to enter personal details
User enters his personal details and click on Next button
User updates his market preferences and click on Next button
User is redirected to Dashboard then account should be activated
Verify the Web Self Service Registration in CC&B
